NUCLEAR REACTOR
• For controlled process we use nuclear reactors, we use Control
rods as cadmium, boron silver, indium or zirconium to absorb
excess neutrons.
• Heavy water D2O(Deuterium oxide), graphite are used as a
neutron moderator to slow down neutrons,
• Coolant in a nuclear reactor is used to remove heat generated from
