• Basophils are the least (0.5-1 per cent)
Monocyte
• Its body is large, diameter about 15~30 μm without granule.
• Function:
 It contains many nonspecific lipase and displays the powerful
phagocytosis.
• Monocytes largest of all is called Policeman of blood and increase
