hospitals.
Feroz Shah Bahmani (1397-1422 A.D.)
• He was a great general
• He defeated the Vijayanagar ruler Deva Raya I.
• He improvised the ports of Chahul and Dabhol.
• He inducted Hindus in administration on a large scale.
• He encouraged the pursuit of Astronomy and built an observatory
near Daultabad.
Ahmad Shah (1422-1435 A.D.)
